exercise.instructions:
1. After the @TEMPLATE@_ResetAppCmd() function protoype definition add the @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd() definition:
    bool @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd(void *ObjDataPtr, const CFE_MSG_Message_t *MsgPtr);
    Note this isn't required to compile the code, but is good practice if the function needs to be accessed by a unit test.

1. After the last CMDMGR_RegisterFunc() add
    CMDMGR_RegisterFunc(CMDMGR_OBJ, @TEMPLATE@_SET_PARAM_CC, NULL, @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd, sizeof(@TEMPLATE@_SetParam_CmdPayload_t));

Note @TEMPLATE@_SET_PARAM_CMD_CC is generated by the EDS toolchain
